  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>If you need some time to relax...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Everyone needs a break. That's ok.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lie back and chill while you clean and polish every last smudge of dirt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305530/extras/143698defab44b03b874d1f5f66d8eaa.poster.avif?t=1748698075\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305530/extras/143698defab44b03b874d1f5f66d8eaa.webm?t=1748698075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305530/extras/143698defab44b03b874d1f5f66d8eaa.mp4?t=1748698075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Manage your cleaning store</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know all the town's customers, negotiate the sale offers, and try to pay your bills on time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features -</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean away all the dirt from various items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haggle on your items' price to get out with more profit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know different characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play fun mini-games on your PC</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go hardcore cleaning mode with a speedrun timer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the game with any gamepad or with the mouse and keyboard (recommended)</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>If you need some time to relax...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Everyone needs a break. That's ok.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lie back and chill while you clean and polish every last smudge of dirt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305530/extras/143698defab44b03b874d1f5f66d8eaa.poster.avif?t=1748698075\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305530/extras/143698defab44b03b874d1f5f66d8eaa.webm?t=1748698075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305530/extras/143698defab44b03b874d1f5f66d8eaa.mp4?t=1748698075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Manage your cleaning store</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know all the town's customers, negotiate the sale offers, and try to pay your bills on time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features -</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean away all the dirt from various items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haggle on your items' price to get out with more profit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know different characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play fun mini-games on your PC</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go hardcore cleaning mode with a speedrun timer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the game with any gamepad or with the mouse and keyboard (recommended)</p></li></ul>",
